headline: Cboe Launches Index Datasets on Snowflake Marketplace, Further Expanding Access via the Cloud
summary: Cboe Global Markets, Inc. (Cboe: CBOE), the world's leading derivatives and securities exchange network, today announced the availability of the Cboe Global Indices Feed on Snowflake Marketplace. Joint customers can now find end-of-day summary data and tick data from seven Cboe Global Indices Feed channels on Snowflake Marketplace — available for purchase through Cboe DataShopSM — gaining efficient access to high-quality index data via the cloud.
